    Overview

    Almanak’s agent-centric platform empowers its users to build, train, and manage advanced financial strategies using Swarm of AI Agents. It achieves this by creating and combining the following two components:

    1. Almanak AI Swarm decreases the entry barrier and time-to-market of creation, deployment and discovery of sophisticated financial strategies from months to minutes in a full no-code environment. It’s “democratizing” both the hedge fund stack and access to opportunities it generates. What once took weeks of painstaking development and analysis now takes minutes, fundamentally shifting the bottleneck from human limitations to verifiable, automated intelligence.

    2. Deployment Infrastructure allows anyone to launch a Vault and connect it with a sophisticated systemic financial strategy. Users (LPs) can deposit into the vault, getting exposure to sophisticated strategies, whereas the Vault curator can benefit from Management and performance fees (GP & LP like relation).

    This architecture operates on an "AI-Powered Execution, Human-Led Verification" principle. AI handles coding and alpha identification, while humans provide final verification and control. This hybrid model gives institutional allocators confidence to deploy capital into familiar structures while leveraging AI's unique strengths.

    Target Userbase:
    Target Customers are DeFi native professionals seeking a technological edge (A: Strategy & Vault Curators) , as well as common crypto investors looking for attractive yield opportunities (B: Liquidity Providers).

    Inspired by solutions from the traditional financial markets, Almanak intends to address this challenge by a marketplace where quality strategies will be recently matched with free capital (GP & LP model). To achieve that, the ecosystem distinguishes the aforementioned two key roles: Strategy & Vault Curators and Liquidity Providers.

    • Strategy & Vault Curators - are the primary users of Almanak Agentic AI-Swarm and Vault infrastructure. They use Almanak Agentic AI-Swarm to design, optimize, and manage their own fully variable and deterministic strategies in a no-code environment. In order to get access to the external capital, Curators can deploy their own Vaults, which are then connected with the strategies they created. Similarly to the role of contributors in Bittensor Subnets 1 , Curators are rewarded with Almanak Tokens for delivering high-quality Strategies and connecting them with the Vaults. Connecting the strategy to the Vault and making it accessible for Liquidity Providers allows Strategy & Vault Curators to earn performance and management fees based on the TVL and returns of the Vault, without sharing the strategy code.
    • Liquidity Providers - passive users of the platform. Liquidity Providers can deposit capital directly into the Vaults to get exposure to fully AI-designed algorithmic strategies, administered by the Strategy & Vault Curators. In exchange for their deposits, Liquidity Providers are being issued with a fully fungible and composable position in the Vault, which can be further used within the DeFi ecosystem.
